# Extension Features Guide

## Core Features

### Transcript Processing
- Real-time transcript extraction from YouTube videos
- Multi-language support
- Status indicators for transcript availability

### Voice Interaction
- Built-in microphone controls with audio visualization
- Voice-to-text conversion
- AI-powered response generation using Gemini API

### User Interface
- Draggable floating window interface
- Collapsible components
- Video playback controls
- Settings management

## Implementation Details
- Uses React components for modular UI
- Zustand for state management
- Tailwind CSS with DaisyUI for styling
- Google Generative AI for content processing

## Feature Locations
- Main UI: [entrypoints/content/App.tsx](mdc:entrypoints/content/App.tsx)
- Settings: [entrypoints/content/settings.tsx](mdc:entrypoints/content/settings.tsx)
